 <title>Prerequisites</title>
 <conbody>
  <p>Before you can read MySQL binary logs to generate change data capture records, you must
            complete the following prerequisites:<ul id="ul_gcz_k4x_1bb">
                <li>Configure MySQL server to use row-based logging.</li>
                <li>Install the MySQL JDBC driver.</li>
            </ul></p>
 </conbody>
